A man from Mdantsane was arrested at the weekend after he allegedly stole, killed, skinned, then ate his neighbour s dog. Siphiwo Monco and an unidentified friend, who is still on the run from police, were caught by dog owner Njongo Mgayi just hours after the pet disappeared on Friday from his NU2 home.For the full story get a copy of the Dispatch or subscribe to our e-Edition for the complete newspaper with jobs, classifieds, crosswords, TV schedules and back editions